Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:41.15,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這裡不是世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:42.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}想想你是從哪裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:45.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如何走到了今日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.49,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}失敗!!
